MaiaKoda Language Development Roadmap: Claude Implementation Specification

Executive Summary

This specification defines a multi-phase development plan for creating the MaiaKoda language ecosystem. Each phase produces a working, testable artifact that builds upon previous phases.

```yaml
phases:
  phase_0:
    name: "Bootstrap Compiler (Zig)"
    output: "maia-koda-bootstrap"
    language: "Zig"
    duration: "4-6 weeks"
    
  phase_1:
    name: "Self-Hosted Compiler"
    output: "maia-koda-selfhosted"
    language: "MaiaKoda"
    duration: "6-8 weeks"
    
  phase_2:
    name: "Modal Editor (Kakoune-style)"
    output: "mkedit"
    language: "MaiaKoda"
    duration: "4-5 weeks"
    
  phase_3:
    name: "TUI Documentation Reader"
    output: "mkdocs"
    language: "Koda"
    duration: "2-3 weeks"
```

